the same reaction to music...

1433
01:56:37,046 --> 01:56:38,843
...as you do to sex and violence?

1434
01:56:39,048 --> 01:56:43,417
No, missus. You see, it's not
all music. It's just the Ninth.

1435
01:56:43,653 --> 01:56:45,416
