is, like, trying to snuff it.

1440
01:56:59,869 --> 01:57:04,272
-I beg your pardon?
-Snuff it. Death, I mean.

1441
01:57:04,540 --> 01:57:07,065
I just want to die peacefully...

1442
01:57:07,577 --> 01:57:09,875
...like, with no pain.

1443
01:57:10,680 --> 01:57:12,580
